privateJob.title: IBM Associate Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for Various  Posts
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Associate Consultant

Description:

IBM  has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Associate Consultant. If you are finding jobs in Bangalore then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by IBM  can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles, and responsibilities are given below. IBM is dealing with software products. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  • Written test
  • Group Discussion
  • Personal Interview

Role and responsibility:

  • Studying the existing business process, End User support, to resolve any specific challenges faced by customer across all the processes
  • Understand the requirements/business process of customers … provide a solution from a process standpoint.
  • For custom requirements, analyze and provide the solution, write a functional specification, coordinate with technical team to get them developed and tested
  • As a part of the support team, analyze and provide solutions to incidents/service requests and coordinate with the larger team, if needed, to provide resolution
  • These are some of the roles and responsibilities for one post. You should check for each post shown in apply now link

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for IBM  job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the Engineering from a recognized university to apply for the application IBM Associate Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • Good understanding of SAP product portfolio
  • Good understanding of the respective industry / Line of business process
  • Functional expertise – SD / MM / FI
  • Technical knowhow – SAP BW / BW4 HANA would be a plus
  • Technical expertise – SAP BASIS / SOLMAN
  • Experience – 0 -2 years
  • Should have studied ERP system/ SAP architecture as part of their academic/ technical course curriculum
  • 2 simulation projects in absence of LIVE project experience

IBM Associate Consultant Payscale :

  • The basic Payscale at IBM for the post of an Associate consultant is 39000/month

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for IBM Associate Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for IBM  Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the IBM Associate Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website link.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
